    <string name="about_how_to_use_title">📖 How to Use</string>
    <string name="about_how_to_use_desc">1. Save trusted numbers in \'Contacts\'.\n2. Allow Camera &amp; Location permissions.\n3. Shake phone 3 times to trigger SOS.\n4. App will silently send location &amp; photo link.\n5. View saved evidence photos in Profile-(History).</string>
