    <string name="tips_main_title">Safety &amp; Tips</string>
    <string name="tips_shortcut_title">🚨 Secret SOS Shortcut</string>
    <string name="tips_shortcut_desc">In an emergency, you don\'t need to open the app. Simply shake your phone rapidly 3 times. The app will silently capture an evidence photo using the back camera, upload it securely, and send your live location and photo link to your trusted contacts via SMS.</string>
    <string name="tips_defense_title">🛡️ Basic Self-Defense</string>
    <string name="tips_defense_desc">• Be Aware: Keep your phone away and pay attention to your surroundings when walking alone.\n\n• Trust Instincts: If a place or person feels unsafe, leave immediately. Don\'t worry about being polite.\n\n• Use Voice: Shout \'FIRE\' instead of \'HELP\'. People are more likely to respond quickly.\n\n• Weak Points: If attacked, strike hard at the attacker\'s eyes, nose, or throat.\n\n• Share Location: Always keep your live location shared with trusted family members.\n\n• Keep Distance: Maintain a safe 2-3 step distance from strangers.</string>
